HTI is leading the way with cloud computing in the hospitality sector, having recently integrated eRes with Nebula – HTI’s new cloud-based offering. The product of this integration is a new cloud-based CRS and Channel Management offering, including BookNow – a fully integrated Internet booking engine (IBE), ideal for both individual properties as well as hotel chains (multi-property booking engine). In the following video, Rory Montgomery, HTI Executive Director, and Werner Kok, HTI Technical Director, discuss their integrated cloud solutions and their benefits to clients. These benefits include accessibility of information, improved support and service, reduced cost of infrastructure, and more. The video below details everything you need to know about HTI’s cloud offerings.  For more information, please visit the HTI website. This article was published in partnership with HTI.